quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  47,10,"Aâni ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d imezwura nnsen? Issexv iten Öebbi. Am akka i ijehliyen"
  47,11,"Ayagi, acku Öebbi d bab n wid iumnen. Ijehliyen, ur asen illi bab"
  47,12,"Ih, Öebbi ad Issekcem wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Wid ijehlen zehhun, teppen akken itepp lmal. D times ay d leqôaô nnsen"
  47,13,"Acêal n at temdinin i yifen, di tezmert, tamdint i k id iéâan! Nesqucc iten, ur asen illi useîîaô"
  47,14,"Day win illan ar ubeggen n Mass is, am win, iwumi ppucebbêen yir igiten is, u iîîafaôen chawi nnsen"
  47,15,"Amek tga Loennet i ippuwaââden i wid ipêezziben: degs isaffen n waman ur nxeppeô, isaffen n yi$i ur tfessed lbenna s, isaffen n ccôab aéidan i wid itessen, isaffen n tament ippuneqqan. Degs, i nitni, yal ppemôa, akked ssmaê n Mass nnsen. Day am wid iwekkôen di tmes; sswan ten s waman ippayzagen, ara icergen afwad nnsen"
  47,16,"Llan garasen wid i k issemêasen. Sifat ff$en d s$uôek, ad inin i wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni: \"d acu id inna kan, llinna\"? Wigi d wid iwumi Isle$ Öebbi ulawen, teddun kan d chawi nnsen"
  47,17,"Wid ipwanhan, Irna asen nnhaya, Ifka yasen aêezzeb nnsen"
  47,18,"Day la pôaoun kan imir, a ten id ias, deqzalla? Ni$ usant ed licaôat is. Ma iusa d $uôsen, iwumi t usmekti nnsen"
  47,19,"Cfu ar, s tidep, ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi; ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik, akked wid n lmumnin, argaz tameîîut. Öebbi Iéôa anda têebkem, akked wanda tberrkem"
  47,20,"La qqaôen wid iumnen: \"a lemmer a d ters tsuôep\"! Maca, mi d ters tsuôep tuêkimt, ideg id ipwader umennu$, a pwaliv at wul iblan, la k id pmuqulen s tiî n win tessexcawat tmeppant. Yif it i nitni"
  47,21,"wannuz, akked wawal uwqim. Mi ipwagzem ôôay, ma ssawlen tidep ar Öebbi yif it i nitni"
  47,22,"Day maççi, ma twexxôem, ahat a ppesfesdem tamurt, a pfaôqem alag nnwen"
  47,23,"Wigi d wid i Ixza Öebbi; Isgugem iten, Isder$el iéôi nnsen"
  47,24,"Day ur pmeyyizen ara Leqwôan, ne$ u$alent tsergal $ef wulawen"
  47,25,"Ih, wid ixedâan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya $uôsen, ikellex iten Cciîan. Iooa ten tallit"
  47,26,"Ayagi, acku nitni nnan i wid iugin ayen d Issader Öebbi: \"ad awen na$ awal di kra n lumuô\". Öebbi Iéôa lesrar nnsen"
  47,27,"Amek ihi, ma ddment lmalayek leôwaê nnsen, la ten kkatent ar udmawen nnsen, iârar nnsen"
  47,28,"Akka, ihi, ddan akked wayen isserfayen Öebbi. Ugin llza S. D$a Isseôxes igiten nnsen"
  47,29,"Ne$ $ilen at wul amehzul, ard awez$i, ur d Issuffu$ ara Öebbi leb$wev nnsen"
  47,30,"Lemmer i £ ihwi, ad ak ten id Nessken, war ccekk, a ten tâaqlev ar udem nnsen, a ten tâaqlev ar ûûenf umeslay. Öebbi Issen igiten nnwen"
  47,31,"S tidep, a kwen Njeôôeb, alamma Nessen imjuhad, akked iûebôiyen, segwen. A Njeôôeb isallen nnwen"
  47,32,"Ih, wid ijehlen, issefôa$en abrid n Öebbi, i inuqmen Amazan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya $uôsen, ur vuôôen Öebbi s wacemma. Ad Isseôxes igiten nnsen"